OL,3,CWorkers could see #6,000 boost to
OL,4,Cpension pots under Government plans
OL,6,FMillions of workers could see a #6,000
OL,7,Fboost to their retirement pots as part
OL,8,Fof Government plans to double the
OL,9,Fnumber of UK pension megafunds by 2030.
OL,11,FReforms in the Pension Schemes Bill
OL,12,Fpropose that multi-employer defined
OL,13,Fcontribution pension schemes and local
OL,14,Fgovernment pension scheme pools
OL,15,Foperate at megafund level, managing at
OL,16,Fleast #25 billion in assets within the
OL,17,Fnext five years.
